
Grate 1 clove garlic, or pound it smooth with a pinch of salt. Melt 6 tbsp
butter and add the garlic, 1/4 c tahini, 2-3 tbsp lime juice, 2 tbsp soy sauce,
and 1 tsp sesame oil. Whisk together until smooth (it will take a while to 
emulsify everything fully). Taste, and adjust salt and lime juice.


Ingredients:
6 tbsp unsalted butter
1/4 c tahini
2-3 tbsp lime juice
2 tbsp soy sauce
1 tsp sesame oil
1 clove garlic
